## 五、Attempt JSON 结构

```json
{
  "run_id": "uuid-...",
  "commit_hash": "abc123",
  "parent_hash": "def456",
  "agent_id": "agent-3",
  "task_id": "sql-inject-01",
  "score_bundle": {
    "scores": {
      "correctness": { "value": 0.85, "name": "correctness", "explanation": "参数化查询覆盖率 85%" },
      "security": { "value": 0.92, "name": "security", "explanation": "通过所有 OWASP 测试用例" }
    },
    "aggregated": 0.88,
    "feedback": "SQL参数化做得好，但遗漏了存储过程场景"
  },
  "evolution_signals": [
    { "source": "grader", "dimensions": { "correctness": 0.85, "security": 0.92 } },
    { "source": "judge", "dimensions": { "approach": "promising", "coverage": 0.7 } }
  ],
  "status": "improved",
  "message": "v3: 增加了存储过程的参数化检测",
  "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:30:00Z",
  "shared_state_hash": "git-sha-..."
}
```

**其他 Agent 的使用方式**：
1. recall 发现某 task 的高分 attempt
2. 拉取 attempt JSON → 阅读 feedback、evolution_signals、策略描述
3. 作为自己任务的参考输入

