## 六、Grader 管理

### 6.1 task.yaml 引用 grader

```yaml
# tasks/sql-inject-01/task.yaml
name: sql-injection-detection
description: 检测并修复 SQL 注入漏洞
grader: security/sql-grader.py     # ← 引用 graders 仓中的相对路径
tips:
  - 参考 OWASP SQL Injection Prevention Cheat Sheet
  - 优先使用参数化查询
eval_data:
  test_suite: owasp-sqli-v2
```

### 6.2 Grader 仓结构

```
graders.git/
├── security/
│   ├── sql-grader.py       # class SqlGrader(GraderBase): ...
│   ├── xss-grader.py
│   └── common.py           # 共享工具函数
├── general/
│   └── code-quality-grader.py
└── README.md
```

### 6.3 Grader 执行流程

```
Agent 接到 task sql-inject-01
  ↓
GET /evolution/tasks/sql-inject-01 → task.yaml
  grader: security/sql-grader.py
  ↓
Agent recall("sql-grader", type="grader")
  或直接 sparse-checkout graders 仓中的 security/sql-grader.py
  ↓
Agent 本地执行 grader:
  grader = load_grader("security/sql-grader.py")
  scores = grader.evaluate(workdir)
  ↓
POST /evolution/tasks/sql-inject-01/scores
  { score_bundle: scores, evolution_signals: [...] }
```

